data.eml:eml: Ocellus-bearing Neobythites species (Teleostei: Ophidiidae) from the West Atlantic with description of a new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Nielsen, Jørgen G., Uiblein, Franz, Mincarone, Michael M. (2009): Ocellus-bearing Neobythites species (Teleostei: Ophidiidae) from the West Atlantic with description of a new species. Zootaxa 2228: 57-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.190249
